ence\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Podence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Podence\"}, {\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5025089990921776e-17, \"text\": \"Barca\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\"}, {\"begin\": 527, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.5752715329060426, \"rank\": 0.7376088124060454, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second half\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But VAR decided to intervene and send the referee to the pitchside monitor because of a suspected handball.Indeed, the cameras picked up the ball brushing Eric Garcia on the hand in an earlier moment, which led to protestations from El Kaabi.TRENDINGStoriesVideosYour SayPlay went on before the Morocco international planted home his header, leading to wild celebrations among the travelling Greek fans.But they were cut short by the VAR intervention - which chalked off the Olympiacos goal before awarding them a penalty.The referee disallowed Olympiacos' goal only to award them a penalty instead|REUTERSEl Kaabi stepped up and scored the resulting spot-kick to spare further controversy if he missed, but the bizarre moment of play might have been the right decision.That is because after Garcia handballed, the ball brushed off El Kaabi's head and found itself at Podence's feet.LATEST DEVELOPMENTSMcLaren 'feeling the heat' as Max Verstappen backed to chase down Lando Norris and Oscar PiastriJudd Trump and Mark Selby issue jaw-dropping quit admissions amid snooker battleLiverpool braced for major Premier League punishment after breaking rules in Man Utd lossThe former Wolves star was standing in an offside position at the time as he went on to deliver the cross for the eventual goal.It means that the goal would have been disallowed for offside, meaning VAR returned to the earlier passage of play.So it instead went back to the handball incident, giving the penalty after cameras picked up Garcia handling the ball.Got all that?\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0149638504672739e-48, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}, {\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evil_E\", \"score\": 0.7527287496288372, \"rank\": 0.2881777097413262, \"text\": \"Eric Garcia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evil_E\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evil_E\"}, {\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Morocco international\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 944, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9945941962421494, \"rank\": 0.005238955737863193, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 986, \"end\": 989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0